org.javaToAvalla.model.terms

Class JavaTerm

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.javaToAvalla.model.terms.Term
      • org.javaToAvalla.model.terms.JavaTerm
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JavaArgumentTerm, JavaAssertionTerm

    public abstract class JavaTerm
extends Term
    Abstract class representing a generic Java term.

    JavaTerm extends the Term class and provides a common structure for Java-specific terms, including a type field that describes the term's type. It serves as a base class for more specialized Java terms.
